21:45.805 --> 21:49.934
♪ ♪

21:49.934 --> 21:53.104
[truck rumbles past]

21:53.104 --> 21:55.857
[dishes clanging]

21:55.857 --> 21:57.066
[Walter]
Just a half a day left.

21:58.359 --> 21:59.193
Maybe a day.

22:00.028 --> 22:01.779
All right, I'll see you later,
Jodi.

22:01.779 --> 22:03.197
[Jodi] See you, Walter.

22:03.197 --> 22:05.116
