22:44.781 --> 22:51.662
♪ ♪

22:54.290 --> 22:55.458
[exhales sharply]

22:55.458 --> 22:58.461
[dark music]

22:58.461 --> 23:05.176
♪ ♪

23:05.176 --> 23:07.929
- [car horn blares]
- [tires screech]

23:07.929 --> 23:09.597
- [metal crunches]
- [glass shatters]

23:10.973 --> 23:15.144
[panting]

23:17.939 --> 23:20.942
[faint overlapping
conversations]

23:22.068 --> 23:23.569
[clicks tongue]
I feel fine now.

23:23.569 --> 23:25.363
[Dr. Zamani] Uh-huh.

23:25.363 --> 23:27.198
Just must have been dizzy
or something.

23:28.157 --> 23:29.325
[Dr. Zamani]
Does that happen a lot?

23:30.409 --> 23:31.536
Sometimes, yeah.

23:32.787 --> 23:35.540
I had this brain injury
back when I served.

23:35.540 --> 23:36.791
What kind of injury?

23:37.875 --> 23:39.043
Well, actually, I'm not sure.

23:40.294 --> 23:41.921
We hit an IED,

23:41.921 --> 23:44.632
and I guess they had to
cut me open back here.

23:44.632 --> 23:46.050
Hmm.
May I?

23:46.050 --> 23:46.926
Yeah.

23:49.387 --> 23:52.640
I lost a few years
and some of my memory, but...

23:52.640 --> 23:54.308
I'm feeling better now.

23:54.308 --> 23:55.476
I'm basically fine.

23:56.811 --> 23:58.396
Yeah.

23:58.396 --> 24:00.523
- What?
- Nothing. I just...

24:00.523 --> 24:02.483
you said you had surgery
back there.

24:02.483 --> 24:03.359
Yeah.

24:04.277 --> 24:07.071
Well...d...
that's what my mom told me.

24:07.071 --> 24:08.489
I just didn't see a scar.

24:08.489 --> 24:09.824
But you're feeling okay now,
though?

24:09.824 --> 24:11.951
[indistinct chatter]

24:11.951 --> 24:13.286
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

24:13.286 --> 24:15.037
[unnerving piano music]

24:15.037 --> 24:15.913
I feel fine.

24:15.913 --> 24:20.710
♪ ♪

